Package Entities

package Entities
  • Class
    Description
    Booking
    Represents a movie booking.
    Cinema
    Represents a cinema hall located at a particular cineplex.
    CinemaClass
    Represents a group of constants related to the type of available cinema classes.
    Cineplex
    Represents a cineplex outlet.
    ContentRating
    Represents a group of constants related to the movie content ratings.
    DayType
    Represents a group of constants related to the type of days in a week.
    Holiday
    Represents a public holiday.
    Movie
    Represents a movie listing.
    MovieGenre
    Represents a group of constants related to the different movie genres available.
    MovieType
    Represents a group of constants related to the type of movie (i.e., 2D, 3D).
    Review
    Represents a movie review made by a movie-goer.
    Seat
    Represents a cinema seat.
    ShowingStatus
    Represents a group of constants related to the showing status of a movie (i.e., Coming Soon, Now Showing).
    ShowTime
    Represents a movie showtime.
    ShowTimeStatus
    Represents a group of constants related to the status of a showtime (i.e., Available, Sold Out).
    Ticket
    Represents a movie ticket.
    TicketType
    Represents a group of constants related to the age of the movie-goer purchasing a ticket (i.e., Standard/Adult, Senior, Student).
